ove -item: to move file or folder to new location                                                                            
1-organize files by moving them to new folder                                                                                    
Move-item  -path  "c:\ downloads \ file. Txt " -destination document                                             
2-consolidate multiple folders into one                                                                                                
Move-item -path "c:  \old folder " -destination   new folder                                                            
      Copy-item: to copy file or folder                                                                                                        
1-backup file                                                                                                                                             
Copy-item  -path  "c :\my file .txt" destination                                                                                    
2-copy a directory and its contents                                                                                                        
Copy-item  -path "c \my  file " -destination  backup -recurse                                                            
